The driver sync_timer provides syncronization for an asterisk+dahdi system.
Before building kernel dahdi sourses should be installed on the system to the
/usr/src/ and compiled. Complete path to dahdi sources is
/usr/src/dahdi-linux-complete<dahdi source version>

To build driver execute command as user root:
make DAHDI_DIR=/usr/src/dahdi-linux-complete<dahdi source version>

Install:
make install


